VYHY DBUr-YHVH 'aLY L'aMUr.
BN-'aDM DBUr 'aL-BNY-'yMK V'aMUrTh 'aLYHM 'aUrTSh KY-'aBY'a 'yLYH ChUrB VLQChV 'yM-H'aUrTSh 'aYSh 'aChD MQTShYHM VNThNV 'aThV LHM LTShPhH.
VUr'aH 'aTh-HChUrB B'aH 'yL-H'aUrTSh VThQ'y BShVPhUr VHZHYUr 'aTh-H'yM.
VShM'y HShM'y 'aTh-QVL HShVPhUr VL'a NZHUr VThBV'a ChUrB VThQChHV DMV BUr'aShV YHYH.
'aTh QVL HShVPhUr ShM'y VL'a NZHUr DMV BV YHYH VHV'a NZHUr NPhShV MLT.
VHTShPhH KY-YUr'aH 'aTh-HChUrB B'aH VL'a-ThQ'y BShVPhUr VH'yM L'a-NZHUr VThBV'a ChUrB VThQCh MHM NPhSh HV'a B'yVNV NLQCh VDMV MYD-HTShPhH 'aDUrSh.
V'aThH BN-'aDM TShPhH NThThYK LBYTh YShUr'aL VShM'yTh MPhY DBUr VHZHUrTh 'aThM MMNY.
B'aMUrY LUrSh'y UrSh'y MVTh ThMVTh VL'a DBUrTh LHZHYUr UrSh'y MDUrKV HV'a UrSh'y B'yVNV YMVTh VDMV MYDK 'aBQSh.
V'aThH KY-HZHUrTh UrSh'y MDUrKV LShVB MMNH VL'a-ShB MDUrKV HV'a B'yVNV YMVTh V'aThH NPhShK HTShLTh.
V'aThH BN-'aDM 'aMUr 'aL-BYTh YShUr'aL KN 'aMUrThM L'aMUr KY-PhSh'yYNV VChT'aThYNV 'yLYNV VBM 'aNChNV NMQYM V'aYK NChYH.
'aMUr 'aLYHM ChY-'aNY N'aM 'aDNY YHVH 'aM-'aChPhTSh BMVTh HUrSh'y KY 'aM-BShVB UrSh'y MDUrKV VChYH ShVBV ShVBV MDUrKYKM HUr'yYM VLMH ThMVThV BYTh YShUr'aL.
V'aThH BN-'aDM 'aMUr 'aL-BNY-'yMK TShDQTh HTShDYQ L'a ThTShYLNV BYVM PhSh'yV VUrSh'yTh HUrSh'y L'a-YKShL BH BYVM ShVBV MUrSh'yV VTShDYQ L'a YVKL LChYVTh BH BYVM ChT'aThV.
B'aMUrY LTShDYQ ChYH YChYH VHV'a-BTCh 'yL-TShDQThV V'yShH 'yVL KL-TShDQThV L'a ThZKUrNH VB'yVLV 'aShUr-'yShH BV YMVTh.
VB'aMUrY LUrSh'y MVTh ThMVTh VShB MChT'aThV V'yShH MShPhT VTShDQH.
ChBL YShYB UrSh'y GZLH YShLM BChQVTh HChYYM HLK LBLThY 'yShVTh 'yVL ChYV YChYH L'a YMVTh.
KL-ChT'aThV 'aShUr ChT'a L'a ThZKUrNH LV MShPhT VTShDQH 'yShH ChYV YChYH.
V'aMUrV BNY 'yMK L'a YThKN DUrK 'aDNY VHMH DUrKM L'a-YThKN.
BShVB-TShDYQ MTShDQThV V'yShH 'yVL VMTh BHM.
VBShVB UrSh'y MUrSh'yThV V'yShH MShPhT VTShDQH 'yLYHM HV'a YChYH.
V'aMUrThM L'a YThKN DUrK 'aDNY 'aYSh KDUrKYV 'aShPhVT 'aThKM BYTh YShUr'aL.
VYHY BShThY 'yShUrH ShNH B'yShUrY BChMShH LChDSh LGLVThNV B'a-'aLY HPhLYT MYUrVShLM L'aMUr HKThH H'yYUr.
VYD-YHVH HYThH 'aLY B'yUrB LPhNY BV'a HPhLYT VYPhThCh 'aTh-PhY 'yD-BV'a 'aLY BBQUr VYPhThCh PhY VL'a N'aLMThY 'yVD.
VYHY DBUr-YHVH 'aLY L'aMUr.
BN-'aDM YShBY HChUrBVTh H'aLH 'yL-'aDMTh YShUr'aL 'aMUrYM L'aMUr 'aChD HYH 'aBUrHM VYYUrSh 'aTh-H'aUrTSh V'aNChNV UrBYM LNV NThNH H'aUrTSh LMVUrShH.
LKN 'aMUr 'aLYHM KH-'aMUr 'aDNY YHVH 'yL-HDM Th'aKLV V'yYNKM ThSh'aV 'aL- GLVLYKM VDM ThShPhKV VH'aUrTSh ThYUrShV.
'yMDThM 'yL-ChUrBKM 'yShYThN ThV'yBH V'aYSh 'aTh-'aShTh Ur'yHV TM'aThM VH'aUrTSh ThYUrShV.
KH-Th'aMUr 'aLHM KH-'aMUr 'aDNY YHVH ChY-'aNY 'aM-L'a 'aShUr BChUrBVTh BChUrB YPhLV V'aShUr 'yL-PhNY HShDH LChYH NThThYV L'aKLV V'aShUr BMTShDVTh VBM'yUrVTh BDBUr YMVThV.
VNThThY 'aTh-H'aUrTSh ShMMH VMShMH VNShBTh G'aVN 'yZH VShMMV HUrY YShUr'aL M'aYN 'yVBUr.
VYD'yV KY-'aNY YHVH BThThY 'aTh-H'aUrTSh ShMMH VMShMH 'yL KL-ThV'yBThM 'aShUr 'yShV.
V'aThH BN-'aDM BNY 'yMK HNDBUrYM BK 'aTShL HQYUrVTh VBPhThChY HBThYM VDBUr- ChD 'aTh-'aChD 'aYSh 'aTh-'aChYV L'aMUr B'aV-N'a VShM'yV MH HDBUr HYVTSh'a M'aTh YHVH.
VYBV'aV 'aLYK KMBV'a-'yM VYShBV LPhNYK 'yMY VShM'yV 'aTh-DBUrYK V'aVThM L'a Y'yShV KY-'yGBYM BPhYHM HMH 'yShYM 'aChUrY BTSh'yM LBM HLK.
VHNK LHM KShYUr 'yGBYM YPhH QVL VMTB NGN VShM'yV 'aTh-DBUrYK V'yShYM 'aYNM 'aVThM.
